* Selenium Class 10

* How to Handle calendars:
  1. Click on calendar
  2. Locate the Month & get the text
  3. If the desired text is not visible -> We will keep clicking on next & keep updating the text of the month
  4. As soon as we find our desired month -> grab all the cells from the table
  5. Loop through the cells
  6. Once the cell value is matched with our condition -> click on the matched date.

* Why do we need screenshots in testing?
  - In testing it is very important to take screenshots
    in order to prove that our test case covered certain functionality.

* Taking screenshots in selenium:
  - In order to take screenshots we will be using -> TakeScreenShot Interface

